        <mxCell id="jgNrpzvnfALyjRSeVGWO-14" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;strong&gt;Why api gateway instead of clients calling services directly?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;If clients called services directly, every service would need to implement auth, rate limitation itself. The gateway centralizes this. It&#39;s also your single point to add logging, monitoring, and analytics for all traffic." vertex="1">
